"# acme Engineering Report — Week of Jun 29 – Jul 5, 2026

## Executive Summary

A strong week focused on the API: rate limiting landed and review flow stayed healthy.

## Key Numbers

| | |
|---|---:|
| PRs merged | 4 |
| Merged to production | 1 |
| Merged to staging | 3 |
| PRs opened | 3 |
