| Issues closed | 1 |
| Commits (work branches) | 76 |
| Lines changed (merged PRs) | +6,960 / −5,150 |
| Active contributors | 5 |
| Active repos | 3 / 3 |
| Median time to merge | 28.5 h |

## Highlights

- 🕰️ **Oldest open PR**: [api#7](https://github.com/acme/api/pull/7) “Refactor billing” by @dave — open for 66 days.
- 🚢 **Top merger**: @bob (2).
- 🔍 **Top reviewer**: @bob (2).
- 🧊 **PRs awaiting first review** (2 total ≥7d):
  - [api#7](https://github.com/acme/api/pull/7) “Refactor billing” by @dave — 66 days
  - [web#8](https://github.com/acme/web/pull/8) “Migrate to Vite” by @alice — 16 days
- 🐘 **Biggest PR merged**: [web#3](https://github.com/acme/web/pull/3) “New dashboard” by @carol (+1,500/−200).
- ⚡ **Fastest first review**: @carol reviewed [api#1](https://github.com/acme/api/pull/1) in 45 min.
- 🎉 **First-time contributors**: @dave — welcome!
- 🔥 **Most active repo**: **api** (2 PRs merged, 42 commits).

## Repository Activity

