**web** (2)

- [web#4](https://github.com/acme/web/pull/4) “Bump deps” — @depbot[bot] (+5,000/−4,800, Jul 1)
- [web#3](https://github.com/acme/web/pull/3) “New dashboard” — @carol (+1,500/−200, Jul 3)

